title: Gene Deckerhoff with PA #92Noon!
description: Gene has called games for Florida State hoops/football and Tampa Bay Bucs for 46 years collectively. It's Uncle Gene. And he's calling his second Super Bowl for the Bucs on Sunday, so we caught up with him ahead of the cannons firing at Raymond James
